WEBVTT

00:07.740 --> 00:08.939
It's cold and windy.

00:08.940 --> 00:10.629
Madam, take care of your health.

00:10.630 --> 00:11.659
I'll be fine.

00:11.660 --> 00:13.210
I'm not that weak.

00:13.860 --> 00:15.160
But I'm really worried

00:15.710 --> 00:17.290
about Ansu.

00:18.270 --> 00:20.730
She must be heartbroken

00:21.040 --> 00:22.800
But it's not convenient for me
to visit her.

00:23.440 --> 00:25.130
Go and buy her some tonic.

00:25.310 --> 00:26.450
Yes, Madam.

00:26.860 --> 00:28.000
Who is it?

00:32.380 --> 00:33.520
Directress Su?

00:33.980 --> 00:35.370
What are you trying to do?

00:41.670 --> 00:42.810
Zhao?

00:43.620 --> 00:44.579
You can leave us.

00:44.580 --> 00:45.840
Yes, Princess.

00:52.830 --> 00:54.970
I'd like to ask Madam something.

00:55.300 --> 00:58.160
Where did you get this silver hairpin?

01:00.260 --> 01:03.539
Madam, my mother asked me
to give this to you.

01:03.540 --> 01:04.579
Thank you for your help.

01:04.580 --> 01:05.840
I cannot accept this.

01:12.340 --> 01:14.130
A mother and her son gave it to me.

01:15.230 --> 01:17.610
When Yantang saved them,

01:17.950 --> 01:20.970
their village
had already been attacked by bandits.

01:21.980 --> 01:24.050
The boy's arm was burned.

01:24.060 --> 01:25.690
But luckily he was saved in time.

01:26.110 --> 01:27.250
Otherwise,

01:27.670 --> 01:29.410
he would have died on the streets.

01:43.510 --> 01:45.080
The people you saved

01:45.750 --> 01:49.640
were my mother and younger brother.

01:56.830 --> 01:59.440
Madam, could you take me to them?

02:10.050 --> 02:13.030
(Zhaowen Bookstore)

02:40.830 --> 02:42.349
Your mother and brother

02:42.350 --> 02:44.210
(To Su Yan)
are doing well in Liaodong.

02:44.860 --> 02:46.229
As long as you stay loyal,

02:46.230 --> 02:49.440
I will take good care of your family.

02:51.910 --> 02:54.090
(I will never forget the kindness)

02:54.230 --> 02:55.760
(you showed the Su Family.)

02:56.860 --> 02:58.629
I'm willing to serve you faithfully

02:58.630 --> 02:59.930
until my dying day.

03:14.140 --> 03:16.840
Madam, please don't tell them I was here

03:17.510 --> 03:19.160
to avoid any complications.

03:19.860 --> 03:21.000
Don't worry.

03:24.890 --> 03:26.840
I'll get going now, Madam.

03:29.260 --> 03:30.400
Yan.

03:36.300 --> 03:37.440
Yan!

03:40.630 --> 03:42.210
- Yan...
- Mother.

03:42.740 --> 03:43.880
Mother.

03:45.580 --> 03:47.210
I was deceived by a treacherous person.

03:48.510 --> 03:50.250
I didn't know you and Brother suffered

03:50.740 --> 03:52.490
so much.

03:53.190 --> 03:54.760
Yan,

03:57.300 --> 03:59.189
I've finally found you.

03:59.190 --> 04:00.330
Mother,

04:00.700 --> 04:04.250
please live well with my brother.

04:11.230 --> 04:12.159
Madam.

04:12.160 --> 04:13.300
Get up quickly.

04:14.300 --> 04:17.370
Madam, you saved

04:17.950 --> 04:19.370
my mother and brother

04:19.510 --> 04:21.370
and helped them settle down.

04:21.700 --> 04:23.320
I will never forget

04:24.100 --> 04:26.200
such kindness.

04:28.310 --> 04:30.050
If I ever get the chance,

04:31.750 --> 04:32.890
I will repay this kindness

04:33.700 --> 04:35.760
a thousand times over.

06:03.130 --> 06:07.329
=Blossom=
(Adapted from the novel "Blossom" by Zhi Zhi)

06:07.330 --> 06:10.409
=Episode 30=

06:10.410 --> 06:13.430
(Natural Grace and Talent)

06:21.140 --> 06:22.400
Madam, what are you doing?

06:23.160 --> 06:24.400
I'm making glutinous rice balls.

06:24.940 --> 06:27.210
I nearly forgot
the palace banquet is around the corner.

06:27.220 --> 06:28.160
That's right.

06:29.220 --> 06:30.360
By the way,

06:30.580 --> 06:32.069
we must not be careless

06:32.070 --> 06:33.920
now that Lord Qing is returning
to the capital.

06:34.780 --> 06:35.869
The more evidence we gather,

06:35.870 --> 06:37.320
the closer we get to safety.

06:37.700 --> 06:40.099
We need to find out
what cards Lord Qing is holding.

06:40.100 --> 06:41.219
Being far away,

06:41.220 --> 06:43.250
he can't quickly grasp the situation
in the palace.

06:43.390 --> 06:46.259
So he must have important allies here,

06:46.260 --> 06:47.440
and not just one.

06:48.660 --> 06:51.640
It's too difficult for us to interfere
with palace matters

06:52.260 --> 06:54.640
unless we leverage
the Eastern Palace's influence.

06:55.750 --> 06:58.690
But the Crown Prince is very stubborn,
and I can't get through to him.

06:58.780 --> 06:59.930
It doesn't matter.

07:00.750 --> 07:03.880
Lord Qing can use our family
to target you.

07:04.020 --> 07:06.080
We can use that method
to our advantage too.

07:07.660 --> 07:11.880
The Crown Princess invited me
to discuss the banquet at the palace.

07:11.950 --> 07:13.320
This is a good opportunity.

07:13.550 --> 07:16.370
Lord Qing and the Crown Prince
also invited me to hunt.

07:16.700 --> 07:18.170
I'll pick you up after the hunt ends.

07:51.650 --> 07:54.170
Eating glutinous rice balls together
is quite interesting too.

07:54.660 --> 07:56.000
What a clever idea.

07:56.430 --> 07:58.069
No wonder Mother specifically instructed

07:58.070 --> 08:01.050
to let you make the arrangements
for the palace banquet.

08:01.140 --> 08:03.389
But as her daughter-in-law,

08:03.390 --> 08:05.960
I'm not as thoughtful
and understanding as you.

08:09.510 --> 08:10.760
Since it's a state banquet,

08:10.990 --> 08:13.880
it naturally honors the Empress
and the Crown Princess.

08:13.990 --> 08:16.050
I'm only lending a hand.

08:16.780 --> 08:19.640
These glutinous rice balls
may look novel.

08:19.930 --> 08:21.890
But kneading the dough
and preparing the fillings

08:21.900 --> 08:23.690
rely on the Imperial Kitchen.

08:26.870 --> 08:29.400
It's the Eastern Palace hosting
the banquet after all.

08:29.750 --> 08:32.290
The Empress doesn't like rigid banquets.

08:33.430 --> 08:34.570
These...

08:35.980 --> 08:39.400
How about focusing on elegance?

08:41.280 --> 08:43.630
The Music Office can change
the first piece of performance

08:43.640 --> 08:46.400
to "Song of the Clear River"
or "Hymn to the Emperor."

08:46.460 --> 08:51.130
The Imperial Food Service can also prepare
dishes using the best produce

08:51.190 --> 08:52.680
from this year's harvest.

08:53.980 --> 08:55.610
So when His Majesty asks,

08:55.740 --> 08:57.400
it will also please him.

09:00.620 --> 09:02.370
Proceed as the Duchess suggested.

09:02.380 --> 09:03.820
- Yes, Your Highness.
- Yes, Your Highness.

09:04.500 --> 09:05.760
My archery skills aren't great.

09:07.670 --> 09:09.610
So I'd appreciate
your guidance, Brother.

09:10.380 --> 09:11.970
If you want to show off,

09:12.060 --> 09:14.220
you should do it in front of Father.

09:15.090 --> 09:16.700
On this hunting ground,

09:16.850 --> 09:18.160
you're picking the wrong person.

09:24.190 --> 09:25.330
That's right.

09:27.670 --> 09:29.730
I can never forget

09:30.620 --> 09:32.250
Yantang's blindfolded archery.

09:33.310 --> 09:34.450
Yantang,

09:34.740 --> 09:36.090
my brother excels in literature

09:36.430 --> 09:37.570
while I, in martial arts.

09:37.830 --> 09:42.450
Do you prefer literature
or martial arts nowadays?

09:45.470 --> 09:47.250
My only preference now

09:48.110 --> 09:49.400
is peace at home.

09:50.040 --> 09:51.520
To be able to spend time with my wife,

09:51.580 --> 09:53.400
watching plays, admiring lanterns,

09:53.870 --> 09:55.160
and living a peaceful life

09:55.830 --> 09:56.970
are enough for me.

09:57.460 --> 10:00.000
Ah, Yantang, you've learned the art
of deflecting questions.

10:00.550 --> 10:02.280
Balancing family peace

10:02.790 --> 10:04.250
and court politics

10:04.620 --> 10:06.280
is possible.

10:06.570 --> 10:07.569
Look at the Crown Prince.

10:07.570 --> 10:09.210
Your alliance for power

10:10.820 --> 10:12.400
isn't my concern.

10:13.980 --> 10:15.920
But it greatly affects you, Brother!

10:21.430 --> 10:25.330
How many supporters
do you still have at court?

10:26.620 --> 10:28.850
And how many are questioning
or impeaching you?

10:30.500 --> 10:32.370
Since you're discussing
royal family matters,

10:32.700 --> 10:34.160
I shouldn't be listening.

10:34.790 --> 10:36.029
I'll take my leave.

10:36.030 --> 10:37.170
Song Mo!

10:37.380 --> 10:39.210
As the Commander of the Imperial Guard,

10:39.830 --> 10:41.880
it's your duty
to protect the royal family.

10:41.980 --> 10:43.490
If anything happens to the Crown Prince

10:43.620 --> 10:45.640
or me today,

10:46.980 --> 10:48.379
you won't escape responsibility.

10:48.380 --> 10:49.520
Youting!

10:49.860 --> 10:52.680
You don't even try to hide
your treasonous intentions, do you?

10:52.880 --> 10:54.200
I could kill you

10:55.100 --> 10:56.880
for what you just said.

10:57.190 --> 10:58.339
You always like

10:58.340 --> 10:59.730
to accuse people

11:00.220 --> 11:02.280
without evidence.

11:02.310 --> 11:04.370
But accusations of treason

11:04.710 --> 11:06.200
require proof.

11:07.200 --> 11:10.210
Even if someone did plan a rebellion,

11:10.550 --> 11:12.800
given the current situation,

11:12.950 --> 11:14.760
giving up the position of heir

11:15.100 --> 11:16.680
to a capable person

11:17.340 --> 11:19.280
could save the people and the state

11:19.550 --> 11:21.210
from suffering.

11:21.270 --> 11:22.219
How dare you!

11:22.220 --> 11:23.269
Imperial Guards, listen up!

11:23.270 --> 11:24.219
- Yes!
- Yes!

11:24.220 --> 11:26.730
All soldiers turn your backs!

11:27.150 --> 11:29.280
Anyone who listens or watches

11:29.360 --> 11:30.549
will face military punishment!

11:30.550 --> 11:31.690
- Yes!
- Yes!

11:42.860 --> 11:45.090
His Highness is truly magnanimous.

11:45.150 --> 11:47.880
Lord Song admires him for that.

11:49.670 --> 11:51.549
Only a scholar

11:51.550 --> 11:53.520
could speak so eloquently

11:53.620 --> 11:55.520
about such a stubborn person.

11:58.220 --> 12:00.040
Every wife in the world

12:00.220 --> 12:04.160
would obey and agree.

12:04.740 --> 12:06.730
But they all scold their husbands
in their hearts.

12:27.220 --> 12:28.360
Your Highness,

12:29.190 --> 12:30.680
are you pregnant?

12:33.310 --> 12:34.850
How did you know?

12:35.550 --> 12:37.850
This season's shad fish is the freshest.

12:38.220 --> 12:40.640
But you find it too fishy.

12:40.740 --> 12:42.160
When pregnant,

12:42.270 --> 12:44.619
a person's sense of smell is heightened

12:44.620 --> 12:47.280
and their food preferences change.

12:49.550 --> 12:50.880
I am like that too.

12:56.140 --> 12:57.880
The imperial physician
diagnosed me earlier.

12:58.310 --> 13:00.680
He said I have a weak body,

13:01.190 --> 13:02.450
making it hard to conceive.

13:02.980 --> 13:04.640
That's why I didn't announce
my pregnancy.

13:07.740 --> 13:09.160
I still feel very nauseated.

13:09.460 --> 13:11.000
Eunuch Wang,

13:11.100 --> 13:13.250
please bring me a magnolia branch.

13:13.310 --> 13:14.450
Yes, Your Highness.

13:17.430 --> 13:19.789
Pick that one for me.

13:19.790 --> 13:20.930
Yes, sir. Watch out!

13:27.380 --> 13:28.520
Watch out!

13:34.220 --> 13:35.360
(It's him.)

13:35.950 --> 13:38.260
(If the Crown Princess gives birth
to a prince next year,)

13:38.580 --> 13:40.920
(the Crown Prince's position
will be secure.)

13:41.190 --> 13:44.090
(Lord Qing will surely rebel.)

13:46.810 --> 13:47.950
Your Highness.

13:52.890 --> 13:54.510
The Crown Princess is very weak.

13:55.250 --> 13:56.409
Take her to the palace hall.

13:56.410 --> 13:57.910
Quickly, fetch the imperial physician.

13:57.920 --> 13:59.190
Your Grace, be cautious.

13:59.370 --> 14:01.819
The Crown Princess
is pregnant after all.

14:01.820 --> 14:03.210
Shouldn't we wait for the physician

14:03.220 --> 14:04.809
- before making a diagnosis?
- It'll be too late.

14:04.810 --> 14:06.180
I must administer acupuncture now.

14:06.200 --> 14:07.490
Please reconsider, Your Grace.

14:08.010 --> 14:10.550
Are you defying orders?

14:12.930 --> 14:14.270
I dare not.

14:27.810 --> 14:29.329
You've got plenty of soldiers.

14:29.330 --> 14:30.769
But I came alone.

14:30.770 --> 14:32.169
If something really happens today,

14:32.170 --> 14:35.270
what will the court officials think
when they find out?

14:36.450 --> 14:37.670
Your Highnesses,

14:37.690 --> 14:39.009
these are different times.

14:39.010 --> 14:41.569
You can't fight like you did
when you were kids.

14:41.570 --> 14:42.689
Every punch now

14:42.690 --> 14:44.470
affects the state.

14:44.490 --> 14:45.710
Please reconsider your actions.

14:45.810 --> 14:46.889
Song Mo!

14:46.890 --> 14:48.990
You always helped me in fights before.

14:49.050 --> 14:50.510
Who will you help now?

14:54.530 --> 14:55.670
Crown Prince.

15:00.330 --> 15:01.910
See that, Crown Prince?

15:02.290 --> 15:04.169
Yantang is always on my side.

15:04.170 --> 15:05.310
Lord Qing.

15:13.430 --> 15:14.329
- Song Mo!
- Song Mo!

15:14.330 --> 15:15.920
- Are you out of your mind?
- Are you out of your mind?

15:18.650 --> 15:21.329
Haven't I treated you
and your son well enough?

15:21.330 --> 15:23.510
I allowed you to participate
in political discussions.

15:24.010 --> 15:25.689
Youting has vast lands

15:25.690 --> 15:28.390
and high income,
much more than Yousheng.

15:28.690 --> 15:30.950
Can't you be content?

15:31.250 --> 15:33.150
What more do you want?

15:40.970 --> 15:43.230
If Father truly despises us,

15:44.050 --> 15:45.390
you could order our deaths.

15:48.770 --> 15:52.590
But don't wrong my heart.

15:59.170 --> 16:00.790
After three years apart,

16:02.010 --> 16:05.710
I never thought
what I longed for day and night

16:05.890 --> 16:07.830
would turn out like this.

16:09.490 --> 16:10.630
Your Majesty,

16:10.970 --> 16:12.870
I am ashamed of myself.

16:12.930 --> 16:15.030
I will resign from my position
in the central palace.

16:15.410 --> 16:17.750
Please strip Youting of his title
and make him a commoner.

16:18.290 --> 16:21.870
My son and I only wish for peace.

16:27.100 --> 16:30.590
Your Majesty, please calm down
for your health's sake.

16:31.010 --> 16:33.020
Official Lu has arrived!

16:38.770 --> 16:40.849
How's the Crown Prince?

16:40.850 --> 16:41.989
Your Majesty,

16:41.990 --> 16:43.470
I've been to the Eastern Palace.

16:43.540 --> 16:45.680
The Crown Prince isn't badly injured

16:45.770 --> 16:46.990
and is not in danger.

16:53.780 --> 16:55.440
For goodness sake, Song Mo.

16:55.600 --> 16:57.750
I can't believe you helped
that jerk to hit me!

16:58.400 --> 16:59.540
I will remember this.

17:02.450 --> 17:04.070
If Yantang hadn't interfered,

17:04.210 --> 17:05.149
you would have lost

17:05.150 --> 17:07.010
a limb or two.

17:09.040 --> 17:10.180
You're welcome.

17:11.660 --> 17:12.679
See that?

17:12.680 --> 17:14.110
He's even proud of himself.

17:14.120 --> 17:15.910
Do you have no respect left
for your monarch?

17:15.920 --> 17:17.020
How insolent!

17:20.440 --> 17:23.150
If Dou Zhao hadn't been here

17:23.200 --> 17:25.230
to perform acupuncture
and medication in time,

17:25.570 --> 17:26.810
your son

17:27.250 --> 17:28.630
would not have survived.

17:29.050 --> 17:30.750
Your Highness,
you give me too much credit.

17:31.020 --> 17:32.870
It's just my duty.

17:33.890 --> 17:35.870
Thank you, Duchess.

17:36.210 --> 17:37.750
I know Your Highness

17:37.810 --> 17:39.950
despises underhanded schemes.

17:40.090 --> 17:42.430
But if a nobleman dies
because of such schemes,

17:42.770 --> 17:44.270
what's the point of being noble?

17:45.770 --> 17:47.430
Lord Qing is back in the capital,

17:47.690 --> 17:50.390
aiming to eliminate

17:50.530 --> 17:51.830
Your Highness and Yantang.

17:52.410 --> 17:53.609
Since you know

17:53.610 --> 17:55.390
the truth about Duke of Ding's death,

17:55.810 --> 17:56.950
revealing it

17:57.050 --> 17:58.550
and exposing Lord Qing's allies

17:58.890 --> 18:00.230
could be your safeguard.

18:05.520 --> 18:07.900
I swore before Father

18:08.370 --> 18:09.510
never

18:10.180 --> 18:11.450
to speak of it.

18:13.510 --> 18:14.650
Well,

18:15.060 --> 18:17.950
you swore, but I didn't.

18:18.450 --> 18:19.590
If you don't tell,

18:20.090 --> 18:21.230
I will.

18:21.610 --> 18:22.449
Don't you dare!

18:22.450 --> 18:23.990
- If you tell, I'll...
- Divorce me?

18:24.650 --> 18:25.790
Sure, go ahead.

18:25.890 --> 18:27.750
I'll take my child and remarry.

18:28.010 --> 18:29.590
I won't let us die with you.

18:35.410 --> 18:36.630
He won't speak

18:37.170 --> 18:39.710
because it involves royal secrets.

18:40.010 --> 18:43.630
Even a word would cause chaos
in the state.

18:44.300 --> 18:46.390
The Emperor never intended
to kill the Duke of Ding.

18:46.690 --> 18:49.670
He ordered the Shadow Guard to escort
the Duke of Ding to the capital

18:50.170 --> 18:52.630
because the emperor

18:52.650 --> 18:54.110
was gravely ill

18:54.850 --> 18:56.470
and feared his death was near.

18:58.610 --> 18:59.750
At that time,

19:00.810 --> 19:02.190
Father was very sick.

19:02.950 --> 19:05.400
The Duke of Ding pacified the pirates
and opened up sea trade,

19:05.410 --> 19:07.070
which benefited the state.

19:07.080 --> 19:09.610
Although he provided disaster relief
and defied imperial orders,

19:09.620 --> 19:11.230
they were a timely help to the people.

19:12.330 --> 19:14.750
Why did you suspect him

19:14.810 --> 19:16.110
and have him escorted back here?

19:17.130 --> 19:19.689
Jiang Meisun is the only person
in this world

19:19.690 --> 19:22.169
whom I can completely trust.

19:22.170 --> 19:24.030
Why would I suspect him?

19:24.930 --> 19:26.350
Then why...

19:27.370 --> 19:29.590
He obeys and trusts me.

19:29.650 --> 19:33.550
But will he obey and trust you
in the future?

19:35.250 --> 19:36.390
You

19:36.890 --> 19:39.710
don't know how to manage ministers.

19:41.450 --> 19:43.009
Pleading for him in private

19:43.010 --> 19:44.550
does no good.

19:45.330 --> 19:48.310
Wait until I reprimand him,

19:49.130 --> 19:51.470
imprison him, and strip his title.

19:52.010 --> 19:54.870
Then you can plead
for his innocence in court.

19:55.330 --> 19:57.750
That way, he will be indebted to you

19:57.850 --> 20:02.270
and be loyal to you.

20:04.230 --> 20:06.070
Duke of Ding is loyal and just.

20:06.410 --> 20:09.750
I don't want to humiliate and subdue him
with power tactics.

20:10.330 --> 20:12.110
I can visit him sincerely

20:12.450 --> 20:13.710
and win his trust.

20:15.810 --> 20:17.630
A father knows his son best.

20:18.090 --> 20:20.070
You have a kind heart

20:20.170 --> 20:21.910
and will be a benevolent ruler.

20:23.170 --> 20:25.070
But kindness alone

20:25.970 --> 20:28.670
won't secure the state.

20:31.450 --> 20:32.670
Come closer.

20:37.850 --> 20:40.390
My illness fluctuates.

20:41.010 --> 20:42.750
If something happens,

20:43.690 --> 20:45.590
Lizhen in the North

20:46.370 --> 20:49.310
and the pirates in the South
will invade again.

20:49.930 --> 20:52.870
The feudal princes will be restless.

20:54.410 --> 20:57.470
I would rather Meisun hate me,

20:58.370 --> 21:02.470
but you must hold onto
this valuable ally.

21:04.690 --> 21:06.409
After my demise...

21:06.410 --> 21:07.449
Father.

21:07.450 --> 21:08.830
After you ascend the throne,

21:08.930 --> 21:10.609
release him from prison

21:10.610 --> 21:12.390
and restore his power.

21:12.610 --> 21:14.230
Only then

21:15.610 --> 21:17.870
will the country remain stable.

21:18.850 --> 21:20.630
Do you understand,

21:20.850 --> 21:21.990
my son?

21:25.370 --> 21:27.750
If Duke of Ding had reached the capital,

21:28.090 --> 21:29.950
everything would have been fine.

21:30.930 --> 21:34.550
But someone took advantage
of the situation.

21:36.970 --> 21:38.110
Your Highness.

21:40.130 --> 21:41.270
Come in.

21:43.250 --> 21:44.430
Eunuch Wang is here.

21:56.050 --> 21:58.369
Eunuch Wang is closer to Father

21:58.370 --> 22:00.229
and knows more about the circumstances

22:00.230 --> 22:02.070
of Duke of Ding's death.

22:04.010 --> 22:05.150
Eunuch Wang.

22:05.770 --> 22:08.390
Since His Majesty already knew

22:08.490 --> 22:09.910
why was he still convicted?

22:13.090 --> 22:15.330
Because Her Majesty
persuaded His Majesty

22:15.340 --> 22:16.849
that it was too late to change things.

22:16.850 --> 22:19.430
If Duke of Ding was declared innocent,

22:19.810 --> 22:21.310
the public would see it

22:21.690 --> 22:24.030
as the emperor unjustly killing
a loyal subject,

22:24.210 --> 22:26.710
damaging the royal family's reputation.

22:27.610 --> 22:28.750
An emperor

22:29.330 --> 22:31.830
can never be seen making a mistake.

22:35.530 --> 22:36.670
My uncle sacrificed

22:37.210 --> 22:38.889
his life for the emperor.

22:38.890 --> 22:40.310
Yet his loyalty

22:41.130 --> 22:43.150
was less important than saving face.

22:44.250 --> 22:46.270
His Majesty couldn't bear it.

22:46.410 --> 22:48.930
So he gave a lenient sentence,

22:48.950 --> 22:51.249
allowing Duke of Ding's body
to be collected and buried,

22:51.250 --> 22:53.830
and lightly punished the Jiang family.

22:55.050 --> 22:56.470
Thank you, Eunuch Wang.

22:57.090 --> 22:58.510
Given the current situation,

22:58.930 --> 23:01.870
if you two don't work together

23:01.890 --> 23:03.950
to save the state,

23:04.090 --> 23:06.849
the peace and prosperity

23:06.850 --> 23:09.830
that the emperor and Duke of Ding
worked hard to build

23:10.210 --> 23:11.990
will be destroyed.

23:13.290 --> 23:14.790
I've always suspected one thing.

23:15.370 --> 23:17.310
If Lord Qing intends to rebel,

23:18.010 --> 23:19.590
but he's far away in Liaodong.

23:19.970 --> 23:21.169
Even with inside help,

23:21.170 --> 23:23.089
communication would take too long.

23:23.090 --> 23:25.169
How could he react
to changing situations

23:25.170 --> 23:26.510
and give his order without delay?

23:27.010 --> 23:28.590
If I'm not mistaken,

23:29.010 --> 23:30.849
the true mastermind

23:30.850 --> 23:33.950
behind this rebellion isn't Lord Qing

23:34.850 --> 23:36.390
but Her Majesty Wan.

23:36.960 --> 23:38.100
Am I right?

23:38.610 --> 23:39.910
Her Majesty Wan?

23:43.130 --> 23:44.249
The people of Futing

23:44.250 --> 23:46.449
go to Duke of Ding's shrine

23:46.450 --> 23:47.990
and hail him as a hero.

23:48.810 --> 23:50.209
He used his own salary

23:50.210 --> 23:51.830
to give bonuses to the army,

23:52.290 --> 23:54.910
effectively making them
his private army.

23:57.550 --> 23:59.880
When you sent the Crown Prince
to provide disaster relief,

23:59.890 --> 24:02.190
he defied orders and did it himself.

24:02.250 --> 24:04.169
Now, in the people's eyes,

24:04.170 --> 24:06.830
the court is to blame,
and he is credited.

24:07.170 --> 24:09.070
You might as well make him
a feudal prince

24:09.090 --> 24:10.630
and give Futing to him as his fief.

24:10.890 --> 24:12.350
It would've saved a lot of trouble.

24:23.010 --> 24:25.209
(Xuanyue Palace)

24:25.210 --> 24:27.040
You were supposed
to keep an eye on things

24:27.050 --> 24:29.680
and not let the Crown Princess
and Duchess of Ying get too close.

24:29.690 --> 24:31.089
How could you let this happen?

24:31.090 --> 24:32.209
Calm down, Your Majesty.

24:32.210 --> 24:33.550
I failed you.

24:33.610 --> 24:34.689
Please punish me.

24:34.690 --> 24:36.310
Useless thing.

24:36.370 --> 24:37.409
Get out.

24:37.410 --> 24:38.550
Yes, Your Majesty.

24:50.050 --> 24:52.090
Father's illness relapsed
many times over the years.

24:52.890 --> 24:54.190
Each time it relapses,

24:55.170 --> 24:57.489
it's been you working tirelessly,
handling state affairs,

24:57.490 --> 24:58.790
and reviewing memorials.

24:59.010 --> 25:01.070
That's how you develop night blindness.

25:02.730 --> 25:05.470
The imperial physician
repeatedly warned you not to cry.

25:06.210 --> 25:07.990
I was impulsive in the incident

25:08.960 --> 25:10.350
with the Crown Prince today.

25:11.680 --> 25:12.840
I've let you down.

25:20.050 --> 25:21.190
Youting,

25:22.050 --> 25:24.550
I know you've endured humiliation
for years

25:25.290 --> 25:27.630
just to return to my side.

25:27.970 --> 25:29.870
How is this letting me down?

25:30.650 --> 25:31.790
Come.

25:32.170 --> 25:33.310
Get up.

25:42.890 --> 25:45.110
My genuine tears

25:45.450 --> 25:47.070
have long since dried up.

25:48.490 --> 25:50.230
Your father has been a heavy burden

25:50.290 --> 25:52.830
on us for decades.

25:52.850 --> 25:54.609
It's not easy

25:54.610 --> 25:56.670
to replace him.

25:56.690 --> 25:58.230
In times of great importance,

25:58.730 --> 26:00.009
one must remain calm.

26:00.010 --> 26:01.059
But I can't stand

26:01.060 --> 26:02.670
seeing you kneel before him.

26:03.170 --> 26:04.510
With your wisdom and sacrifices

26:04.570 --> 26:06.049
for the country and the royal family

26:06.050 --> 26:08.390
over the years,

26:09.570 --> 26:11.310
it's he who should be kneeling to you.

26:19.130 --> 26:22.670
If this fragile pretense
is about to crumble,

26:23.170 --> 26:25.510
there's no need to keep up this charade.

26:26.610 --> 26:28.110
It's time to act.

26:29.370 --> 26:31.790
The time for the reckoning
I've set for him

26:32.090 --> 26:34.070
is approaching.

26:36.090 --> 26:38.470
I truly want to see

26:38.850 --> 26:40.830
the day the nation falls

26:40.930 --> 26:42.950
and family turns against each other.

26:43.930 --> 26:46.270
Will that selfish, hypocritical man

26:46.570 --> 26:48.270
still have tears left

26:49.250 --> 26:50.470
to shed?

26:52.290 --> 26:54.230
She's meddling in state affairs
to the extent

26:54.250 --> 26:56.369
and even poisoning Father.

26:56.370 --> 26:58.209
Why are you only telling me now?

26:58.210 --> 27:00.830
Because His Majesty
has always been frail.

27:00.890 --> 27:02.230
For these past few decades,

27:02.290 --> 27:04.950
he can no longer do
without the elixirs of the sorcerers.

27:05.250 --> 27:07.430
Her Majesty Wan knows
such a method well.

27:07.650 --> 27:11.070
The elixirs provided
had immediate effects

27:11.290 --> 27:14.110
but drained his vitality.

27:14.330 --> 27:16.350
The doses were so small

27:16.410 --> 27:20.510
that even Official Lu noticed it late.

27:20.690 --> 27:23.390
A mix of poison and medicine
taken over the years.

27:23.650 --> 27:26.390
If we stop giving it without a solution,

27:26.810 --> 27:27.950
I'm afraid...

27:32.490 --> 27:35.230
No wonder His Majesty knew the truth

27:35.290 --> 27:36.990
but had to cover it up.

27:39.890 --> 27:41.150
Your father's life,

27:41.650 --> 27:43.670
the nation, and the throne,

27:44.370 --> 27:46.070
will you save them or not?

27:51.970 --> 27:53.990
If you want to seize power

27:54.050 --> 27:56.569
and trample
on the royal family's dignity,

27:56.570 --> 27:59.910
I will never support you.

28:00.290 --> 28:03.190
The ruler is above his subjects,
the father above the son.

28:03.570 --> 28:05.070
Do you think

28:05.210 --> 28:07.030
royal prestige

28:07.370 --> 28:09.150
is more important
than the injustice suffered

28:09.290 --> 28:11.390
by one person, one family, and an army?

28:11.770 --> 28:14.409
Justice, law, honor,

28:14.410 --> 28:15.449
and morality.

28:15.450 --> 28:16.849
Are these just false idols used

28:16.850 --> 28:18.990
by the royal family
to control the people?

28:19.530 --> 28:20.830
If so,

28:20.930 --> 28:22.969
Song Mo and I have no reason

28:22.970 --> 28:24.409
to serve a foolish and selfish ruler.

28:24.410 --> 28:25.249
Dou Zhao,

28:25.250 --> 28:26.369
how dare you!

28:26.370 --> 28:27.249
Well said!

28:27.250 --> 28:29.010
- I scolded her well, didn't I?
- Dou Zhao,

28:29.010 --> 28:30.350
I'm willing to pay you

28:30.570 --> 28:32.350
to come here and scold him every day.

28:33.930 --> 28:35.070
You...

28:37.720 --> 28:39.270
There's one more thing.

28:39.490 --> 28:41.950
It involves
the Duke of Ying's household.

28:42.810 --> 28:45.929
I once overheard

28:45.930 --> 28:48.270
Lord Qing and Her Majesty Wan talking

28:48.410 --> 28:50.289
in her palace

28:50.290 --> 28:53.569
about a letter from Duke of Ding hidden
at the Duke of Ying's Residence,

28:53.570 --> 28:56.270
that has yet to be found.

28:59.730 --> 29:00.870
I know about that.

29:01.170 --> 29:03.510
His Highness came
to my house looking for that letter.

29:04.410 --> 29:05.569
What is it about?

29:05.570 --> 29:06.910
What's written in the letter?

29:08.250 --> 29:10.070
I don't know the content of the letter.

29:10.130 --> 29:12.230
But I do know the letter is important.

29:12.410 --> 29:15.430
The messenger I captured confessed

29:16.010 --> 29:19.110
that a servant had received the letter.

29:19.210 --> 29:21.569
Despite searching it secretly
several times,

29:21.570 --> 29:22.849
I haven't found it.

29:22.850 --> 29:26.510
And Lord Qing is coveting
this letter too.

29:26.690 --> 29:28.009
So no matter what,

29:28.010 --> 29:30.310
we cannot let Lord Qing
have this letter.

29:31.370 --> 29:32.510
I've already said

29:32.530 --> 29:34.550
what I can.

29:34.650 --> 29:35.849
Whatever both of you decide

29:35.850 --> 29:37.030
will be fate.

29:37.830 --> 29:39.910
I shall take my leave now.

29:40.290 --> 29:41.750
Many thanks, Eunuch Wang.

29:50.050 --> 29:52.200
You've studied the teachings
of Confucius and Mencius.

29:53.250 --> 29:55.049
If idols fall,

29:55.050 --> 29:56.190
rituals collapse,

29:56.410 --> 29:58.009
and everyone rebels

29:58.010 --> 29:59.270
like Chen Sheng and Wu Guang,

29:59.490 --> 30:02.430
can the world still be at peace?

30:02.530 --> 30:03.930
The teachings you speak of

30:03.940 --> 30:06.209
is to have virtuous rulers
like Emperor Yao and Emperor Shun,

30:06.210 --> 30:07.950
and then refine the customs
of the people.

30:08.130 --> 30:10.209
But in reality,
the royal family condones

30:10.210 --> 30:12.030
the nobles taking farmland,
enslaving people,

30:12.040 --> 30:14.080
and leaving
the common folk struggling to survive.

30:14.090 --> 30:15.550
Should we silence them

30:15.810 --> 30:17.510
to make them cheer for us?

30:19.490 --> 30:22.670
The tragedies of the Dou Family,
Song Family, and the royal family

30:22.690 --> 30:24.390
stem from the same source.

30:24.810 --> 30:26.489
The ruler and father are supreme,

30:26.490 --> 30:28.769
while wives, concubines,
and children are lowly.

30:28.770 --> 30:31.649
These lowly ones fight
amongst themselves for dominance.

30:31.650 --> 30:33.169
If we judge everything

30:33.170 --> 30:35.070
based on rank rather
than right and wrong,

30:35.130 --> 30:38.150
schemes and plots will never end.

30:38.650 --> 30:40.670
Rituals and laws are meant
to stabilize hearts.

30:41.290 --> 30:44.030
But if they instead cause chaos,

30:45.050 --> 30:48.110
the state will inevitably fall to ruin.

30:51.730 --> 30:53.430
The people are the foundation
of the state.

30:53.440 --> 30:55.270
If you become a good ruler,

30:55.930 --> 30:59.070
I will help you pacify the country
and eradicate evil.

30:59.330 --> 31:00.750
But under one condition.

31:00.930 --> 31:02.550
It's not blood for blood,

31:02.690 --> 31:04.369
or seizing power.

31:04.370 --> 31:07.230
But for the emperor

31:07.450 --> 31:08.990
to publicly reveal the truth,

31:09.730 --> 31:11.270
restore the loyal's honor,

31:11.770 --> 31:13.430
and console the aggrieved.

31:15.090 --> 31:16.230
If you agree,

31:16.570 --> 31:17.710
then we are allies.

31:18.130 --> 31:19.470
If you don't,

31:20.290 --> 31:22.190
I don't mind having one more enemy.

31:31.930 --> 31:33.070
Song Mo,

31:33.090 --> 31:34.870
are you negotiating terms with me?

31:46.410 --> 31:47.499
It would be a pity

31:47.500 --> 31:48.670
to be just allies.

31:49.090 --> 31:51.790
The Crown Prince and I like
Dou Zhao's character.

31:52.050 --> 31:54.470
What if we arrange a marriage
for our unborn children

31:54.770 --> 31:56.670
and become in-laws too?

31:57.970 --> 31:59.529
- Who wants to be in-laws with him?
- Who wants to be in-laws with him?

31:59.530 --> 32:00.569
He might become

32:00.570 --> 32:02.009
a traitor one day.

32:02.010 --> 32:04.410
Then you must have turned
into a stubborn and foolish ruler.

32:04.970 --> 32:06.870
You have a heroic spirit.

32:07.050 --> 32:08.449
How did you end up

32:08.450 --> 32:10.049
with such an arrogant fool?

32:10.050 --> 32:12.430
Crown Princess,
please keep your husband in check.

32:12.530 --> 32:14.249
He's sharp-tongued, rigid, and arrogant.

32:14.250 --> 32:16.390
Everyone from all walks of life
finds him difficult

32:16.450 --> 32:17.870
to get along with.

32:18.410 --> 32:20.550
Dou Zhao,
keep your husband in check too.

32:20.610 --> 32:21.969
If he continues to be reckless,

32:21.970 --> 32:23.550
you'll end up dead on the streets!

32:25.370 --> 32:26.289
You need

32:26.290 --> 32:28.369
to reflect on yourself.

32:28.370 --> 32:30.649
You've become too self-important

32:30.650 --> 32:33.670
and now you've learned to insult others.

32:35.050 --> 32:36.190
You're right.

32:36.600 --> 32:39.010
I need to reflect on

32:39.370 --> 32:41.070
how I ended up

32:41.090 --> 32:42.590
with a shrew

32:42.890 --> 32:44.030
who sides with others.

32:45.050 --> 32:46.040
A shrew, huh?

32:46.050 --> 32:47.449
- Come, I'll show you.
- Please...

32:47.450 --> 32:48.920
- Tell me who's the shrew.
- I'm sorry.

32:48.930 --> 32:50.430
Sorry, huh?

33:02.370 --> 33:04.230
Why are you still frowning?

33:06.970 --> 33:08.529
Our alliance with the Crown Prince

33:08.530 --> 33:11.169
and distancing from Lord Qing
is ultimately a good thing.

33:11.170 --> 33:12.390
We should be happy about it.

33:16.330 --> 33:18.110
What's bothering you?

33:18.970 --> 33:20.150
I think

33:22.370 --> 33:24.110
the Crown Prince seems to admire you.

33:25.690 --> 33:27.649
Haven't you two only met a few times?

33:27.650 --> 33:29.670
Are you seeing things?

33:29.730 --> 33:32.270
It's the Crown Princess who admires me.

33:35.490 --> 33:36.689
Next time you see him,

33:36.690 --> 33:37.969
don't dress up so nicely.

33:37.970 --> 33:39.490
No need for hairpins or fancy clothes.

33:40.010 --> 33:41.190
Just wear something black.

33:43.210 --> 33:44.350
That won't work either.

33:44.690 --> 33:46.990
You also look beautiful in black
without makeup.

33:49.820 --> 33:51.630
When the Crown Prince
was selecting a consort,

33:51.650 --> 33:54.169
he favored intelligence, resilience,
and extensive knowledge.

33:54.170 --> 33:55.310
Isn't that describing you?

33:56.530 --> 34:00.110
Though everything you say
is unreasonable,

34:00.370 --> 34:02.070
I love hearing every word.

34:05.010 --> 34:06.150
Stop the carriage.

34:19.890 --> 34:21.470
We're not home yet.

34:22.370 --> 34:23.630
Your shoe seems dirty.

34:24.730 --> 34:26.110
No, it's not.

34:31.970 --> 34:32.809
What are you doing?

34:32.810 --> 34:34.070
I understand what I must do now.

34:34.270 --> 34:35.609
This poison needs to be treated.

34:35.610 --> 34:37.099
I want to live long

34:37.100 --> 34:38.989
and take good care of my appearance.

34:38.990 --> 34:40.449
So the Crown Prince feels inferior

34:40.450 --> 34:41.769
when he sees me.

34:41.770 --> 34:42.889
Put me down.

34:42.890 --> 34:44.310
So many people are watching.

34:44.930 --> 34:46.809
I want the whole capital to know

34:46.810 --> 34:49.929
that you, Dou Zhao,
are the Duchess of Ying.

34:49.930 --> 34:51.310
This is embarrassing.

34:51.910 --> 34:53.920
It's not the first time
I've carried you like this.

34:57.610 --> 35:00.710
(Natural Grace and Talent)

35:02.010 --> 35:05.310
I didn't even look at him.

35:06.290 --> 35:08.990
Would that hurt Yousheng?

35:09.850 --> 35:12.310
You're considering the big picture,
Your Majesty.

35:12.810 --> 35:16.529
The Crown Prince will surely understand
your intention.

35:16.530 --> 35:19.470
The Crown Prince and Lord Qing
are of noble status.

35:19.490 --> 35:21.230
They were injured in their fight.

35:21.530 --> 35:24.020
(Palace of Heavenly Majesty)
If this issue is brought to light,

35:24.190 --> 35:25.689
the first to be blamed will be Yantang

35:25.690 --> 35:27.870
who was responsible for their safety.

35:29.170 --> 35:31.830
If he was dismissed,

35:33.330 --> 35:37.990
the court's balance
would be hard to maintain.

35:40.250 --> 35:41.390
Your Majesty,

35:41.890 --> 35:44.830
the medicine is getting cold.

36:04.450 --> 36:06.950
Aren't you performing divination?

36:07.890 --> 36:09.150
No.

36:09.530 --> 36:11.030
I already have

36:13.650 --> 36:15.630
my answer.

36:18.770 --> 36:23.790
(Funeral)

36:29.290 --> 36:31.240
Today is the seventh day
since Anping's passing.

36:32.150 --> 36:34.430
The wives of the officials treat you
as they always have.

36:35.330 --> 36:36.750
At the memorial feast,

36:36.890 --> 36:38.230
they show you nothing but respect.

36:39.370 --> 36:41.190
It's clear that everyone knows

36:41.530 --> 36:44.750
Dong Qi truly deserved his death.

36:47.530 --> 36:49.950
I'd rather have stayed in Futing

36:51.250 --> 36:53.430
as a lowly merchant woman
for my entire life

36:54.410 --> 36:56.510
than be wealthy

36:56.970 --> 36:58.430
and lose my brother

36:59.010 --> 37:00.009
like this.

37:00.010 --> 37:01.449
(Tomb of Miao Anping)

37:01.450 --> 37:03.830
Anping was arrogant.

37:04.130 --> 37:06.830
But he wasn't reckless.

37:08.930 --> 37:10.510
Without striving for a higher position,

37:11.130 --> 37:13.510
we can only watch
our loved ones be bullied.

37:14.930 --> 37:16.790
I was the same in the past.

37:18.290 --> 37:19.430
Now,

37:19.850 --> 37:21.710
as the Commander
of the Tengxiang Guards,

37:22.330 --> 37:23.750
I hold real power

37:23.970 --> 37:25.390
equal to Song Mo.

37:25.450 --> 37:26.630
From now on,

37:27.810 --> 37:29.830
we no longer need to bow to anyone.

37:30.530 --> 37:32.150
The Tengxiang Guards

37:33.010 --> 37:36.390
is lesser-known
among the twenty-six guards unit.

37:36.650 --> 37:38.110
The most crucial aspect of it

37:38.590 --> 37:39.529
is that it controls most

37:39.530 --> 37:41.790
of the grain and warhorse supplies
for the capital.

37:42.050 --> 37:44.030
It may seem like one unimportant unit

37:44.170 --> 37:45.830
that no one is interested in.

37:47.010 --> 37:48.390
But in times of war,

37:48.570 --> 37:50.550
cavalry that can charge

37:50.610 --> 37:52.209
and dominate on the plains

37:52.210 --> 37:53.910
will be the key to victory,

37:54.010 --> 37:55.670
whether on the frontier or elsewhere.

37:57.210 --> 38:01.009
Even if the Imperial Guards
and Shenji Camp have firearms,

38:01.010 --> 38:02.590
they're useless

38:02.890 --> 38:04.830
without horses.

38:07.530 --> 38:09.270
The capital is peaceful now.

38:09.850 --> 38:12.910
But you made it seem it's at war.

38:15.890 --> 38:17.270
But peace today

38:17.690 --> 38:19.230
doesn't guarantee peace tomorrow.

38:20.210 --> 38:21.750
Song Mo faced bandits

38:21.810 --> 38:23.070
as his opportunity.

38:23.450 --> 38:25.230
I'll have mine too.

38:25.650 --> 38:28.750
I only want to protect you
and your parents

38:29.170 --> 38:30.590
when the time comes.

38:33.840 --> 38:34.980
Muyu,

38:35.420 --> 38:38.830
thank you for taking care
of my parents recently.

38:39.040 --> 38:41.080
Climbing the official ladder
often requires favors.

38:41.090 --> 38:43.790
If you need anything, just let me know.

38:47.130 --> 38:51.329
(Tomb of Miao Anping)

38:51.330 --> 38:52.470
One day,

38:54.170 --> 38:56.009
I will repay you a thousandfold.

38:56.010 --> 39:02.289
(Tomb of Miao Anping)

39:02.290 --> 39:04.590
(Duke of Ying's Residence)

39:08.370 --> 39:09.510
Watch your steps.

39:25.090 --> 39:26.830
Does this place look familiar to you?

39:47.530 --> 39:50.750
Your Grace, Madam.
Have some tea.

39:52.650 --> 39:53.790
Have a seat first.

39:56.530 --> 39:57.870
Try to recall.

39:58.930 --> 40:00.590
What were you looking for?

40:03.530 --> 40:04.670
Medicine.

40:06.530 --> 40:07.670
Someone.

40:09.570 --> 40:10.489
Medicine.

40:10.490 --> 40:12.310
Duchess of Ying was ill.

40:12.850 --> 40:14.790
She was gravely ill. Am I right?

40:16.650 --> 40:18.910
She was ill. She took medicine.

40:19.370 --> 40:20.510
A fan.

40:21.850 --> 40:22.990
Fan the stove.

40:23.450 --> 40:24.830
Nine types of herbal medicines.

40:25.330 --> 40:26.670
For six hours.

40:27.290 --> 40:28.430
Fan the stove.

40:28.770 --> 40:30.009
Nine types of herbal medicines.

40:30.010 --> 40:31.470
Was there also a letter?

40:34.730 --> 40:35.870
Letter?

40:38.010 --> 40:39.310
Letter...

40:46.690 --> 40:47.649
Who gave it to whom?

40:47.650 --> 40:49.140
What does it say? Where is the letter?

40:49.810 --> 40:50.950
Letter...

40:54.290 --> 40:55.630
Give the letter to me now.

40:56.130 --> 40:57.270
Letter.

40:57.370 --> 40:58.870
Give the letter to me.

40:59.250 --> 41:00.430
Give it to me.

41:02.650 --> 41:03.790
Here you go.

41:04.730 --> 41:06.750
Madam! Madam!

41:06.930 --> 41:08.470
Duke of Ding sent a letter!

41:09.050 --> 41:10.790
Duke of Ding sent a letter!

41:11.010 --> 41:12.150
Follow her.

41:12.370 --> 41:13.510
Madam!

41:35.010 --> 41:37.190
Madam, Duke of Ding has sent a letter.

41:45.490 --> 41:48.029
My brother is playing his riddles again.

41:48.030 --> 41:48.929
Go,

41:48.930 --> 41:50.070
fetch a pen.

41:50.210 --> 41:51.529
Bring some tea.

41:51.530 --> 41:52.710
Yes, Madam.

41:55.090 --> 41:56.230
Madam!

41:56.250 --> 41:57.750
Why are you coughing blood?

42:01.810 --> 42:02.849
Qi Xia,

42:02.850 --> 42:03.689
quickly.

42:03.690 --> 42:04.889
Dry the painting and hide it.

42:04.890 --> 42:06.329
Tell no one about this.

42:06.330 --> 42:07.980
Don't give it to anyone.

42:07.990 --> 42:09.049
You can only tell Song Mo.

42:09.050 --> 42:10.550
Only Song Mo can know.

42:11.290 --> 42:12.729
- Yes, Madam.
- Go now.

42:12.730 --> 42:13.870
Yes, Madam!

42:17.370 --> 42:18.649
Hide it. I must hide it.

42:18.650 --> 42:20.249
Madam, where should I hide it?

42:20.250 --> 42:21.590
Where should I hide it?

42:22.250 --> 42:23.550
Hide it. I must hide it.

42:24.090 --> 42:25.130
Madam! Madam!

42:25.140 --> 42:26.049
Where should I hide it?

42:26.050 --> 42:27.140
Where could be the perfect spot?

42:27.150 --> 42:28.190
Qi Xia!

42:28.450 --> 42:29.590
Qi Xia!

42:33.770 --> 42:34.910
Yes, Madam.

42:35.570 --> 42:38.409
No place is safe to hide it.

42:38.410 --> 42:41.030
Yes, it will be discovered.

42:41.570 --> 42:42.710
Go.

42:42.730 --> 42:44.390
Help me hang it up.

42:44.490 --> 42:46.110
The more visible, the better.

42:56.970 --> 42:58.110
Let's go.

43:19.570 --> 43:21.409
When the throne changes hands,

43:21.410 --> 43:22.689
you and your husband

43:22.690 --> 43:24.769
won't have a way out.

43:24.770 --> 43:27.209
If I can't be Lord Qing's sharp blade,

43:27.210 --> 43:29.609
I'll be the thorn he must pull out.

43:29.610 --> 43:31.309
Song Mo has gone mad.

43:31.310 --> 43:32.849
He set off explosives in the street,

43:32.850 --> 43:33.889
endangering the people.

43:33.890 --> 43:35.190
Execute him on the spot!

43:35.950 --> 43:40.429
♪I lean in and gaze at you
as calm as serene waves♪

43:40.430 --> 43:44.190
♪I'm aware of the vast
and turbulent world♪

43:44.350 --> 43:48.740
♪Moving forward alone, the expectations
of many are hard to bear♪

43:48.920 --> 43:52.849
♪When the time comes,
I will cast aside a lifetime of pride♪

43:52.850 --> 43:55.829
♪To wear a flower stick for you♪

43:55.830 --> 43:58.039
♪Or perhaps my heart
yearns for the other side♪

43:58.040 --> 44:00.600
♪Yet there's no place for me
to go in the end♪

44:00.650 --> 44:04.220
♪Your presence
my side is irreplaceable♪

44:04.280 --> 44:07.800
♪Like a ship crossing
the desolate river♪

44:07.810 --> 44:11.789
♪That brings me
through a chapter of my life♪

44:11.790 --> 44:15.820
♪You are the light
that saves me in the darkness♪

44:16.260 --> 44:19.720
♪Having you is a blessing♪

44:19.880 --> 44:22.060
♪My heart filled with warmth♪

44:22.080 --> 44:25.910
♪By your side,
I spend the rest of my life♪

44:26.240 --> 44:29.380
♪Your presence
by my side is irreplaceable♪

44:29.920 --> 44:33.330
♪Where my heart yearns
is where I will go♪

44:33.770 --> 44:37.310
♪Breaking waves over the desolate river♪

44:37.510 --> 44:41.179
♪The wind rises as my heart finds peace♪

44:41.180 --> 44:45.520
♪You are the light
that saves me in the darkness♪

44:45.580 --> 44:49.309
♪Having you is a blessing♪

44:49.310 --> 44:52.789
♪Only by being by your side♪

44:52.790 --> 44:57.470
♪I can spend the rest of my life♪

44:57.500 --> 45:01.089
♪Until the waves are all spread out♪

45:01.090 --> 45:05.230
♪And the past sinks into the river♪

45:05.300 --> 45:08.590
♪Always together, looking back♪

45:08.900 --> 45:16.200
♪Only sighing at the commotion♪

45:25.450 --> 45:26.449
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this drama)

45:26.450 --> 45:27.489
(Every medical behaviour involved
and medicine used in the drama)

45:27.490 --> 45:28.670
(is required by the story.
Please don't try this at home)
